  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Regulating persistent organic pollutants if there’s no Brexit deal
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph ">
    How regulation of persistent organic pollutants (POPs) will change if the UK leaves the EU with no deal.

  </p>

  </div>
</div>

<div class="govuk-grid-row">
  <div class="metadata-logo-wrapper">
